  "url": "https://www.tamilmirror.lk/\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd/\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1-\u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8-\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0b95-\u0b92\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc7\u0ba9\u0bcd/175-301289",
  "time_ut": 1659005224,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b92\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc7\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "I would have abolished the executive power completely",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Member of Parliament Dallas Alagaperuma said that if I had been elected as President during the secret ballot held in Parliament, I would have completely abolished the presidential system with executive powers.",
        "Dulles said the above while attending a special press conference held in Colombo today (28).",
        "During the 2019 presidential election, we worked with great commitment to make Gotabaya Rajapaksa the president. During this we got massive support from the youth. However, since the promises made have not been fulfilled, the same youths have taken to the streets and are now struggling. He said that we also fought within the government to take the government to the right path.",
        "We will not deny that we are also responsible for the crisis situation in the country. He said that all 225 members of Parliament should be held accountable for this.",
        "Having been a journalist myself, I know the gravity of the Emergency Act. Parliament does not reflect the views of the people. He also said that we will support any protests that are carried out democratically and respect the law."
      ],
